     (target cold-instance OAuth refresh).
  3. Record per-call: total_ms, oauth_ms, xav_ms, app_ms, instance_id,
     oauth_cache_hit (bool).
  4. Produce sprints/02/S02-T1-server-timing.md with: Method · Per-call
     table · p50/p95 per segment · Cold vs warm delta · Confirmation of
     which hypothesis (A/B/C/D) dominates.

